metadata.name: 01-Olena
metadata.description:
"Olena" was born in Ukraine in 1999, She grew up in an artistic family of four, She went to the United States to study journalism . After the start of the war, she decided to go back and find her family members, unfortunately has not been able to find them yet. Her weapons are a super modern custumed rifle which she uses to defend herself, As well as a cell phone to record events that took place in Ukraine.

Olena is the first piece from "Guardians of peace" collection which contain 12 guardian.

size: 2300*1900 pixel.
